und":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"부원B","body":"부장님! 공연작품은 어떤 거로 할까요?\n하는 작품에 따라서 출연 여부를 고려해봐야 할 것 같은데요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"부장","body":"듣고 보니 일리가 있네요……\n카오루 씨, 마야 씨.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"네!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode181-002","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"부장","body":"둘한테 공연작품을 맡겨도 될까?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"헉!? 괜찮습니까, 저희 둘이 정해버려도.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode181-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"부장","body":"시라사기 치사토 씨를 잘 아는 둘이라면\n그녀한테 맞는 작품도 잘 알 거야.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"부장","body":"부원들끼리 이런저런 의견을 내는 것보다\n시라사기 치사토 씨를 잘 아는 둘이 생각해보는 게 좋지 않을까 싶어서.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"과연. 그런 거라면 맡겨 주시게.\n나와 치사토는 꽤 오랜 교류이니 말이야.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode181-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"알겠습니다! 카오루 씨, 좋은 작품을 찾아내도록 하지 말입니다!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode181-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"부장","body":"고마워. 그럼 작품이 정해지면 알려주세요.\n그럼 오늘은 해산. 수고하셨습니다.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"부원 일동","body":"수고하셨습니다!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"episode181-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"아아…… 이렇게 문화제가 기다려지는 건\n처음이다! 지금 당장 그날이 됐으면 좋겠구나!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode181-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"심정은 알겠습니다만, 우선 공연할 작품을 정해야 합니다!\n문화제에서 공연하는 작품은 전통적으로 고전 작품을 하는 게\n상례인데 올해는 어떻게 하시겠습니까?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode181-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"고전 작품을 공연하는 건 연극부의 전통이지.\n전통을 지키면서도 더욱더 좋게 만드는 것이 좋지 않겠나?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode181-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"오오…… 카오루 씨가 진지합니다……\n그럼 얼른 부실에 있는 대본 중에서 골라보도록 하지 말입니다.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode181-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"그런데 말입니다…… 정말 저희끼리 작품을\n골라도 괜찮은 겁니까?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode181-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"치사토를 잘 아는 인물로서 일임된 것이야.\n자신을 가져야 하지 않겠나?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode181-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"카오루 씨…… 오늘은 진지하시지 말입니다?\n어디 그럼 치사토 씨한테 어울릴만한 작품을\n찾아보도록 하지 말입니다.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode181-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"어디 보자…… 치사토한테 어울릴만한 거라……\n어떤 게 좋을까.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode181-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"치사토 씨라고 하면…… 청초하면서 귀엽고……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode181-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"성실하고 우아하고…… 그리고 보이지 않는 곳에서 도움을 주는\n숨은 공로자 같은 일면이 있기도 하지 말입니다.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode181-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"으~음, 치사토 씨의 어느 면을 내세우면 좋을까.\n고민되지 말입니다~ 카오루 씨 안에서 치사토 씨의 이미지는\n어떤 느낌이십니까?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode181-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"그렇구나…… 내 안에서 치사토는 한마디로 하면 「덧없다」……일까?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode181-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"으아악, 나왔다~! 정말이지, 그걸론 의미를 모릅니다라고\n일 년이 넘게 계속 말하지 않았습니까~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode181-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"그렇게 말한다 한들……\n후후, 조금만 더 나를 이해해줬으면 좋겠구나, 마야.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode181-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"이래 봬도 꽤 이해하고 있다고는 생각하지 말입니다만……\n그럼 좀 더 구체적인 질문을 하겠습니다.\n치사토 씨한테 어울릴 것 같은 작품은 뭐라고 생각하십니까?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode181-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"그거야 물론 덧없……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode181-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"「덧없다」는 금지이지 말입니다!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode181-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"흐음…… 그럼 「로미오와 줄리엣」은 어떤가?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode181-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"줄리엣의 자유분방하면서도 심지가 강한 면은\n그녀한테 잘 맞을 것 같구나.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode181-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"자유분방…입니까…… 선정 이유가 좀 의외이지 말입니다!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode181-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"그런가?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode181-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"네. 전 치사토 씨가 자유분방한 사람이라고 생각한 적이 없습니다.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode181-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"흠흠, 카오루 씨가 보는 치사토 씨는 그런 사람이었군요~\n전 Pastel * Palettes의 치사토 씨밖에\n몰랐으니까 신선합니다.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode181-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"그 또한 치사토지.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode181-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"분명 치사토 씨랑 오래 알고 지낸 카오루 씨밖에\n모르는 치사토 씨가 있다는 거겠지 말입니다. 부럽지 말입니다.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode181-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"그럼 나는 바로 치사토한테 말을 해보도록 하지.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode181-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"치사토 씨가 받아주시겠습니까?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode181-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"그럼, 물론이지! 분명히 흔쾌하게 OK 해줄 거란다.\n쇠뿔도 단김에 빼는 것. 지금 바로 치사토한테 전화해보마.\n치사토는 나에게 맡겨주렴.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode181-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"네! 그럼 전 공연작품이 정해졌다는 내용을\n부원들한테 보고하겠습니다!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode181-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"치사토 씨가 연기하는 줄리엣이라, 벌써 기대됩니다~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"shame01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode181-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"아아, 치사토, 이제서야 내 전화를 받아주는구나.\n혹시, 일 때문에 바빴던 건가?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode181-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"응? 그런 건 아니라고?\n후후…… 정말이지 무정하구나.\n그대의 그런 자유분방한 모습에는……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motion